data.description: Nicely updated home located in Deerfield Estates.  This home is located minutes from Baylor Scott and White and I-35 with easy access to all that Temple/Belton has to offer.  5 large bedrooms, 3 ba home with 2 living rooms, 2 dining areas, high ceilings and tons of storage.  This home has been updated with new flooring, new granite countertops throughout, new freshly painted cabinets, dry stacked stone fireplace, designer paint and all new fixtures and LED lights throughout.  Enjoy the warm summer nights on the large covered back porch. Owner is a licensed Texas Realtor.
